{"title_page": "J. Jayalalithaa", "text_new": "{{short description|Indian politician and actress}}\n{{EngvarB|date=October 2019}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=October 2019}}\n{{Infobox officeholder\n| name           = J. Jayalalithaa\n| image          = J Jayalalithaa.jpg\n| caption        = J. Jayalalithaa in August 2015\n| office         = 5th [[List of Chief Ministers of Tamil Nadu|Chief Minister of Tamil Nadu]]\n| term_start     = 23 May 2015\n| term_end       = 5 December 2016\n| president      =\n| primeminister  =\n| governor       = [[Konijeti Rosaiah]],<br />[[C. Vidyasagar Rao]]\n| 1blankname     = Speaker\n| 1namedata      =\n| 2blankname     =\n| 2namedata      = \n| predecessor    = [[O. Panneerselvam]]\n| successor      = [[O. Panneerselvam]]\n| constituency   = [[Radhakrishnan Nagar]]\n| term_start1    = 16 May 2011\n| term_end1      = 27 September 2014\n| president1     = \n| primeminister1 = \n| governor1      = [[Surjit Singh Barnala]],<br />[[Konijeti Rosaiah]]\n| 1blankname1    = Speaker\n| 1namedata1     = \n| 2blankname1    = Leader of Opposition\n| 2namedata1     =\n| predecessor1   = [[M. Karunanidhi]]\n| successor1     = [[O. Panneerselvam]]\n| constituency1  = [[Srirangam (state assembly constituency)|Srirangam]]\n| term_start2    = 2 March 2002\n| term_end2      = 12 May 2006\n| president2     = \n| primeminister2 = \n| governor2      = [[P. S. Ramamohan Rao]],<br />[[Surjit Singh Barnala]]\n| 1blankname2    = Speaker\n| 1namedata2     =\n| 2blankname2    = Leader of Opposition\n| 2namedata2     = \n| predecessor2   = [[O. Panneerselvam]]\n| successor2     = [[M. Karunanidhi]]\n| constituency2  = [[Andipatti (state assembly constituency)|Andipatti]]\n| term_start3    = 14 May 2001\n| term_end3      = 21 September 2001\n| president3     =\n| primeminister3 = \n| governor3      = [[Fathima Beevi]],<br />[[C. Rangarajan]] (additional charge)\n| 1blankname3    = Speaker\n| 1namedata3     =\n| 2blankname3    = Leader of Opposition\n| 2namedata3     = 