ian women politicians]]\n[[Category:20th-century Indian politicians]]\n[[Category:21st-century Indian women politicians]]\n[[Category:21st-century Indian politicians]]\n[[Category:20th-century Indian actresses]]\n[[Category:Members of the 12th Tamil Nadu Legislative Assembly]]\n[[Category:Members of the 13th Tamil Nadu Legislative Assembly]]\n[[Category:Members of the 14th Tamil Nadu Legislative Assembly]]\n[[Category:Members of the 15th Tamil Nadu Legislative Assembly]]\n[[Category:State funerals in India]]\n[[Category:Members of the 10th Tamil Nadu Legislative Assembly]]\n", "name_user": "Kowsalya.T.R", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/J._Jayalalithaa"}
